    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, trim the ends from your <strong>Brussels sprouts</strong>,<strong> </strong>then add to a <strong>food processor</strong> and blitz until finely chopped</p><p>Tip: Don't have a food processor? Chop them up as finely as you can!</p>",
