    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>sprouts</strong> to a medium bowl<strong> </strong>with your <strong>dried</strong> <strong>cranberries</strong>,<strong> half </strong>your<strong> mayo</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mix it all together –<strong> </strong>this is your<strong> sprout slaw</strong></p>",
