    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked, put your<strong> bao buns</strong> on a plate and cover them, then <strong>microwave</strong> for<strong> </strong>15-20 secs</p><p>To build your buns, fill each <strong>bao bun</strong> with the<strong> crispy chicken </strong>and top with the<strong> remaining</strong> <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>cranberry sauce</strong> and <strong>crispy onions </strong>– these are your <strong>crispy chicken & cranberry bao buns</strong></p>",
